<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="S" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Swift2" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Swift,</orth> adv. swiftly, rapidly: <cit><quote>Away! As s. as lead,</quote> <bibl n="shak. lll 3.58" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL III, 58</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>courses as s. as thought,</quote> <bibl n="shak. lll 4.3.330" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 3, 330</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>my eyes can look as s. as yours,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mv 3.2.199" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. III, 2, 199</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>skirr away as s. as stones,</quote> <bibl n="shak. h5 4.7.64" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 IV, 7, 64</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>another would fly s., but wanteth wings,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h6 1.1.75" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A I, 1, 75</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>light boats sail s.</quote> <bibl n="shak. tro 2.3.277" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. II, 3, 277</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. tro 5.10.29" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 10, 29</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tit 4.1.3" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. IV, 1, 3</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tit 4.2.172" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 2, 172</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tit 5.2.51" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 2, 51</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 1.5.66" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. I, 5, 66</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 1.3.14" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. I, 3, 14</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 2.2.48" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 2, 48</bibl>. Compar. <emph>--er</emph>: <cit><quote>I do wander every where, --er than the moon's sphere,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mnd 2.1.7" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. II, 1, 7</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>about the wood go --er than the wind,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mnd 3.2.94" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 2, 94</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. mnd 3.2.94" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 2, 94</bibl> <bibl n="shak. mnd 4.1.103" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 1, 103</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h4 1.1.123" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B I, 1, 123</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h4 3.2.282" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 2, 282</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tro 3.2.170" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. III, 2, 170</bibl>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>